               <msContents>
                  <summary>Ptollas reminds Isas that two years have passed since he borrowed an unspecified sum from Ptollas. The latter maintains from start to finish a smooth, courteous, friendly tone, but leaves no doubt that he expects repayment at the earliest opportunity.</summary>
